H0.text: Producers are humans as members of a food web.

H1.text: Consumers are humans considered to be members of a food web.

H2.text: Decomposers are humans as members of a food web.

H3.text: Scavengers are humans considered to be as members of a food web.

A5.text: A heterotroph cannot produce its own food; it takes nutrition from other sources of organic carbon.
